# Environment Variables Template

Copy this file to `.env` and fill in the values for your environment.

## Database Configuration
DATABASE_URL=postgresql://postgres:$$Dut041103@localhost:5432/ai_app_db

## JWT Configuration
# Minimum 32 characters - use a strong random string
# Generate with: python -c "import secrets; print(secrets.token_urlsafe(32))"
SECRET_KEY=mbniguf-vghcVC-YuygtUhYVH-OGyygihl-jU

# JWT algorithm (do not change unless you have a specific reason)
ALGORITHM=HS256

# Token expiry time in minutes (default: 24 hours)
ACCESS_TOKEN_EXPIRE_MINUTES=40

## CORS Configuration (for production, restrict to specific domains)
FRONTEND_URL=http://localhost:3000

## Optional: Email Configuration (for future notifications)
SMTP_HOST=smtp.gmail.com
SMTP_PORT=587
SMTP_USER=your-email@gmail.com
SMTP_PASSWORD=your-app-password
